{"tid":1167330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳美國點名南韓電訊商LG U+  指令停用華為","createTime":"2019-05-23T03:33:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T15:26:43.000Z","uid":227801,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"2d4b6462df608d4f5ba7662a5e05a784ad3bcef5","tid":1167330,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T03:33:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.942882/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Faafn-news%2FNOW.942882%2F2&d=z4MUysNBbosN1Ywc1Uoyo8kuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=ed66a60e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.942882/2</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n南韓《朝鮮日報》引述南韓外交消息報道，美國多次要求南韓禁制使用中國電訊設備商華為的產品，近期更點名使用華為設備南韓電訊商LG U+，指必須不能讓LG U+在南韓國內敏感地區服務，最終要令華為完全從南韓「出局」。<br />\n<br />\n南韓外交部則擔心，禁制華為會遭到中國報復，業界擔心停用華為設備損失達數十億美元，還未計及中國報復帶來的其他損失。<br />\n<br />\n報道又指，美國向南韓外交部表示，為防止華為設備進一步擴散至東亞地區，美國需要三星電子等南韓企業貢獻力量。美國國務院今日(23日)在泰國曼谷，與南韓外交部及南韓企業等召開進軍東盟通訊項目的非公開研討會。(fc/t)"},{"pid":"c5e7f5e652610ff7f75bcf39a7ed254cf0aa041f","tid":1167330,"uid":51828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T03:34:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1b39c685dd3e27ea1f63e979ade64f756860110","tid":1167330,"uid":213597,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T03:35:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ae1f3ba8729f382d3739482223bba72b127a61bd","tid":1167330,"uid":10717,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T03:37:11.000Z","msg":"U+個5g慢撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e475d6639298e37b53d4b82ba8de9761186fd86","tid":1167330,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":